      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Esteemed Sir, ¶  ¶ I am sending you herewith various items ¶  ¶ that ¶  ¶ have been sent to me for you by Dr ¶  ¶ Mueller from Melbourne. No doubt you have already been notified of them by letter, ¶ T...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M64.00.00</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Wilhelm Sonder to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Diederich von Schlechtendal</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>not<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>seen;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>undated letter<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>extracted from Tkach, Neubauer &amp; Roser (2022), Brief<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>38.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The final sentence suggests that the letter was written in December.</p>
               </note>Geehrter Herr,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>sende Ihnen hiermit verschiedene Gegenstände, die mir von Herrn Dr. Müller aus Melbourne für Sie zugestellt sind. Ohne Zweifel sind Sie darüber brieflich schon benachrichtigt, auch wird Herr Dr. Müller seine Wünsche in Bezug auf einige fehlende Bände der Linnaea gegen Sie selbst geäussert haben. Falls Sie etwas an Dr. Müller zu senden haben, bitte ich, es mir im Laufe des Winters zuzustellen, da ich mit dem ersten Frühjahr eine Kiste an ihn<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>befördere. Wollen Sie denn die noch von mir bei Ihnen weilenden Pflanzen Elaeagnus, Sparganium etc. zugleich mitsenden, so wird es mir lieb sein.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>Ich habe das Manuskript<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>zum<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>dritten Bande der Flora capensis abgeliefert u hoffe den Druck in einigen<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>Monaten<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>fertig<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>zu<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>sehen. Harvey’s Krankheit hat auch<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>eine<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>Unterbrechung<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>verursacht. Ich habe die Ankündigung des 2.ten Bandes in Ihrer<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>botan. Zeitung vergebens<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>erwartet<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>oder<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>sollte ich sie<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>übersehen<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>haben<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">—</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Sehr bitter gestimmt hat mich die Behandlung von Prof. H. v. Mohl<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>der mir vor Jahren die Benutzung der in seinem<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>Besitze<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>befindlichen<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>Pflanzen von Krauss zugesagt<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>jetzt<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>aber auf 3 Briefe<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>nicht<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>antwortet<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>meine Bitte, um Mittheilung<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>einer<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>einzigen<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>Pflanze<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>unberücksichtigt<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>lässt und Herrn Dr. Hegelmayer, der sich<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>anbietet, die Beförderung<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>oder<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>Abzeichnung<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>zu<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>übernehmen<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>abschlägige<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>Antwort<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>giebt. Ich habe die Pflanzen<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>unberücksichtigt<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>lassen<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>müssen. Ich<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>habe<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>aller Welt mein Herbarium / zur Disposition gestellt u begreife<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>ein<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>solches<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>Misstrauen von Seiten des Hr. v. Mohl<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>nicht, da doch<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>kein<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>öffentl. Museum oder<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>keine<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>Sammlung<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>durch<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>mich<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>Schaden<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>gelitten hat.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wir haben jetzt einen jungen Hamburger, der in Peru sammelt u schon eine Sendung von ca 100 Species aus der Umgebung von Lima herbefördert hat. Er hat dort jetzt eine hübsche Anstellung u hoffe ich, dass<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>er uns das schöne Land bekannter machen werde, namentlich wenn er erst seine Excursionen in die Gebirge ausdehnen kann.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit dem Wunsche, dass Sie sich wohlbefinden u mit einer Gratulation zum bevorstehenden Jahres wechsel verbleibe ich</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Ihr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>ergebenster</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Esteemed Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am sending you herewith various items<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>have been sent to me for you by Dr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Mueller from Melbourne. No doubt you have already been notified of them by letter,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>There are no letters from M among Schlechtendal's surviving correspondence at Halle.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and Dr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Mueller will also have expressed his wishes to you regarding some missing volumes of the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Linnaea</seg>. If<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>you have anything to send to Dr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Mueller, I ask you to send it to me in the course of the winter, as I will send a box to him with the first spring. If you would like to send the plants of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Elaeagnus</seg>,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Sparganium</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>etc. that you<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>still have with you<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>from me<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>at the same time, I would appreciate it.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have delivered the manuscript for the third volume of the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Flora capensis</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and hope to see the printing finished in a few months. Harvey's illness has also caused an interruption. I have been waiting in vain for the announcement of the 2nd volume in your<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Botanische Zeitung</seg>, or have I overlooked it.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>—<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I am very bitter about the treatment by<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Prof. H. v. Mohl, who years ago promised me the use of the plants of Krauss<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that were<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in his possession but now does not answer three letters, takes no account of my request for the communication of a single plant and gives a negative answer to Dr Hegelmayer who offers to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>undertake the transport or sketching. I have put my herbarium at the disposal of the whole world and do not understand such mistrust on the part of Mr v. Mohl, since no public museum or collection has suffered any damage because of me.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>We now have a young man from Hamburg who is collecting in Peru and has already<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>dispatched<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>a consignment of about 100 species from the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Lima area. He now has a good position<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>there and I hope that he will make this beautiful country better known to us, especially when he can extend his excursions into the mountains.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With the wish that you are well and with felicitations on the forthcoming change of year,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I remain</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">your most devoted</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
      </body>
